{"tid":1187414,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"綾瀨遙水着大解放","createTime":"2019-06-05T15:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T15:39:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a1adb2b9823261a14b9201d43faf0e1696d402af","tid":1187414,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190604/large/04ee2p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190604%2Flarge%2F04ee2p8.jpg&h=fd1c0a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n34歲日本女星綾瀨遙貴為日劇界一線花旦，雖然擁有F Cup上圍，但走紅後近年已惜肉如金，在鏡頭前只作有限度性感滿足粉絲。最近她就為代言的航空公司拍攝全新廣告，罕有地再以泳裝上陣。<br />\n<br />\n綾瀨遙繼去年穿空姐制服替ANA全日空擔任代言人，今年續為該公司推廣全新型號空中巴士的夏威夷航班，她不只在機內瞓身上陣，更穿水着於當地嬉水，並踩單車把驕人上圍表露無遺，十分養眼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jqni0h402o0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJqni0h402o0&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElvGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=b2408ee9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jqni0h402o0</a>"},{"pid":"4e8b17d10ae48c30a2984f04779995038bddf413","tid":1187414,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"睇條撚咩"}]}